      "content": "everything you're saying feels so scripted. i'm not looking for a hotline, i'm just... i'm looking for a way to make the noise stop. it's just this constant, loud, horrible ache. i look at the future and i don't see anything. it's not even scary anymore, it's just exhausting. like i'm just stuck in this loop of hurting and there's no exit. how am i supposed to believe it gets better when everything i knew is just... dead?",
